text:
Ashlee+Evan is an American reality television series on E!. It stars Ashlee Simpson and Evan Ross.[1][2]

Premise [ edit ]

Ashlee+Evan follows Ashlee Simpson and Evan Ross, son of Diana Ross, as they try to balance their lives as the son of one superstar & the host of lipsync battle, new parents, and the pressures of living up to their infamous family names.[3][4]
